user.description:
Step 1 of 2: Enter your WillyWeather API key.

Get your free API key from: {api_url}

Station ID is optional - leave blank to automatically find the closest station to your Home Assistant location.

forecasts.description:
Step 2 of 2: Configure forecast sensors for {station_name}

Weather forecasts are always included. Select optional forecast data below.

Note: All current weather observation sensors are always created.
